		<h1><div id="ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_PageH1Container">
	Outpatient Imaging Center at St. Joseph's
</div></h1>
		
		<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
	<tr>
		<td id="MSOZoneCell_WebPartWPQ3" valign="top" class="s4-wpcell-plain"><table class="s4-wpTopTable" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
			<tr>
				<td valign="top"><div WebPartID="cdbfcbb7-9bcf-4032-a05c-14c62e1ef43a" HasPers="false" id="WebPartWPQ3" width="100%" class="ms-WPBody" allowDelete="false" style="" ><p>St. Joseph’s state-of-the-art Outpatient Imaging Center houses the latest digital imaging technologies to provide comprehensive, accurate diagnostic imaging services.&#160;We&#160;couple outstanding patient care with quality customer&#160;service. A team of board certified radiologists and neuroradiologists, certified technologists and staff provide the highest level of personalized care to each and every patient. </p>
<h2><strong>Radiology Services for Your Convenience</strong> </h2>
<p>The 17,000 square foot center is conveniently located on the first floor of the hospital off Third Avenue just north of Thomas Road. The Outpatient Imaging Center is the entry point of access for all outpatient diagnostic and interventional imaging. We offer: </p>
<ul><li>Complimentary valet parking </li>
<li>Free self parking in the Third Avenue garage with validation </li>
<li>Waiting room concierge for easy check-in and registration </li>
<li>Transportation service to other hospital department destinations<strong>?</strong> </li></ul>
<h2><strong>Comprehensive&#160;Imaging Services</strong> </h2>
<p>Our Outpatient Imaging Center provides multiple imaging services, including: </p>
<ul><li>Women&#39;s Imaging </li>
<li>MRI </li>
<li>Computed Tomography (CT) </li>
<li>Positron Emission Tomography (PET/CT) </li>
<li>Nuclear Medicine </li>
<li>Ultrasound </li>
<li>Diagnostic Radiology </li></ul>
<h2><strong>Learn More about St. Joseph&#39;s Outpatient Imaging Center</strong> </h2>
<p>For more information about our many radiology services or to schedule an appointment, call <strong>602-406-6700.</strong> </p></div></td>
